data.title: L A PRESSMART
data.meta_description:
Specialties: Equipment Specialist...
We specialize in the remarketing of printing presses, bindery equipment and CTP systems. From Heidelberg, Komori, Shinohara, Sakurai, Ryobi, KBA, Man Roland, Solna, Adast, Polar, Muller Martini, Horizon, MBO, Sthal, Challenge, Baum, A.B. Dick, Hamada, Screen, Creo and much more....

We have a large inventory of used presses, duplicators, paper cutters, folders, booklet makers, die cutters, UV coaters, more bindery equipment and CTP systems....

Please look through our website for more info... There are many links to articles and more details. Our website is also updated on a daily basis, please click on the links on top to look at our latest equipment list @ www.lapressmart.com Established in 1998.  We our proud to establish successful relationships with the printers of today. We have adapted to the new print trends and economy and have help printers globally with their equipment needs.
